name: cohort_size.metric
label: Cohort Metric
description: Use in conjuction with the Metric Picker
sql: CASE          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'User Retention' THEN trunc(${percent_user_retention})          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'Average Orders per User' THEN round(${average_orders_per_user},2)          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'Average Spend per User' THEN trunc(${average_spend_per_user})          ELSE NULL        END

label: Order Items Average Orders per User

name: cohort_size.average_spend_per_user
label: Order Items Average Spend per User

name: cohort_size.percent_user_retention
label: Users Percent User Retention
description: number of active users / number of users in the cohort (use with months since signup dimension)

name: cohort_size.cohort
label: Cohort Cohort
description: Use in conjuction with the Cohort Picker

name: cohort_size.format_symbol
label: Cohort Format Symbol
sql: CASE          WHEN ${metric_name} = 'User Retention' THEN '%'          WHEN ${metric_name} = 'Average Spend per User' THEN '$'          WHEN ${metric_name} = 'Cumulative Spend' THEN '$'        END

name: cohort_size.metric_name
label: Cohort Metric Name
sql: CASE          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'User Retention' THEN 'User Retention'          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'Average Orders per User' THEN 'Average Orders per User'          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'Average Spend per User' THEN 'Average Spend per User'          WHEN {% parameter metric_filter %} = 'Cumulative Spend' THEN 'Cumulative Spend'          ELSE NULL        END

name: order_items.months_since_signup
label: Order Items Months Since Signup
description: Months an order occurred since the user first signed up

name: data_tool.primary_metric
label: Data Tool Primary Metric
sql: CASE          WHEN {% parameter primary_metric_filter %} = 'Users' THEN ${users.count}          WHEN {% parameter primary_metric_filter %} = 'Visitors' THEN ${unique_visitors}          WHEN {% parameter primary_metric_filter %} = 'Sessions' THEN ${sessions.count}          WHEN {% parameter primary_metric_filter %} = 'Orders' THEN ${sessions.count_purchase}        END

name: data_tool.second_metric
label: Data Tool Second Metric
sql: CASE          WHEN {% parameter second_metric_filter %} = 'Bounces' THEN ${sessions.count_bounce_sessions}          WHEN {% parameter second_metric_filter %} = 'Bounce Rate' THEN round((100.0 * ${sessions.percent_bounce_sessions}),2)          WHEN {% parameter second_metric_filter %} = 'Conversion Rate' THEN round((100.0 * ${sessions.conversion_rate}),2)        END

sql: case when ${due_status} = 'Due Date Passed' and ${paid_status} = 'Unpaid' then DATEDIFF(day, ${due_date}, current_date)        else 0      end

name: invoices.paid_days_late
label: Invoices Paid Days Late
description: If paid late, by how many days?
sql: case when ${paid_status} = 'Paid Late' then DATEDIFF(day, ${due_date}, ${paid_date})        when ${paid_status} = 'Unpaid' then null        else 0      end

name: invoices.due_status
label: Invoices Due Status
description: Due=if due within next 7 days; Not Yet Due=if due > next 7 days; Due Date Passed=if due date is in the past
sql: CASEWHEN DATEDIFF(day, current_date, ${due_raw}) < 8 and DATEDIFF(day, current_date, ${due_raw}) > 0 THEN 'Due'WHEN DATEDIFF(day, current_date, ${due_raw}) > 7  THEN 'Not Yet Due'ELSE 'Due Date Passed'END

name: invoices.paid_status
label: Invoices Paid Status
description: Unpaid=no paid date; Paid Late=paid past due date; Prepaid=paid before due date; Paid On Due Date=paid on due date
sql: CASEWHEN ${paid_raw} is null  THEN 'Unpaid'WHEN ${paid_raw}>${due_raw}  THEN 'Paid Late'WHEN ${paid_raw} < ${due_raw}  THEN 'Prepaid'ELSE 'Paid On Due Date'END
